Package kp.company.web

The classes in this package represent the Web Presentation Layer.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddDepartmentForm
    JavaBean form controller that is used to add a new Department to the system.
    AddEmployeeForm
    JavaBean form controller that is used to add a new Employee to the system.
    CompanyBindingInitializer
    Shared WebBindingInitializer for kp_spring01 custom editors.
    CompanyController
    Annotation-driven MultiActionController that handles all non-form URL's.
    EditDepartmentForm
    JavaBean Form controller that is used to edit an existing Department.
    EditEmployeeForm
    JavaBean Form controller that is used to edit an existing Employee.
    FindDepartmentsForm
    JavaBean Form controller that is used to search for Departments by last name.
    StaticContentFilter
    Static content filter.
    TitleEditor
